        <p>The Franmarine Health, Safety, Environmental and Quality (HSEQ) manual forms the basis for the WMS. Our HSEQ Management System is certified by DNV to ISO 9001, ISO 14001 and ISO 45001. FUS are certified under the Scope of Management of diving, integrated underwater and general services provided to the defence, infrastructure, shipping and oil and gas industries.</p>
