        <p>As part of the vessels regular biofouling management practices, Franmarine have been engaged by {{clientName}} to make an application to undertake a {{cleaningTypeText}} to remove all biofouling from underwater surfaces on the vessel '{{vesselName}}'. The scope is scheduled to be completed over {{estimatedDuration}} days, commencing {{proposedStartDate}}.</p>
