            <li>All diving equipment shall be in accordance with AS/NZS 2299.1:2015 at a minimum.</li>
            <li>Risk assessment using the Decision Support Tool for In-Water Cleaning from the Australian anti-fouling and in-water cleaning guidelines - Exposure draft (2025) Department of Agriculture, Fisheries and Forestry, Canberra (hereafter "2025 IWHC draft guidelines") has determined the cleaning method to be used as non-abrasive hand cleaning, in accordance with the updated environmental risk classification framework.</li>
