                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="framework-arrow">▼</div>

            <div class="framework-box">
                <h4>4. APPROVAL PROCESS</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Submit notification package to FPA and DPIRD</li>
                    <li>DPIRD reviews vessel history, confirms acceptable risk</li>
                    <li>Pre-clean inspection by DPIRD-recognised inspector (≥48hrs before clean)</li>
                    <li>DPIRD clearance to proceed</li>
                    <li>If IMS detected → site to DPIRD custody</li>
                    <li>If no IMS → proceed with clean</li>
                    <li>Post-clean inspection</li>
                    <li>Final Report to FPA and DPIRD (≤20 business days)</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

